    <entry>
      <title>数组跳远（加强版）</title>
      <link href="/2024/05/24/%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E8%B7%B3%E8%BF%9C%EF%BC%88%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E7%89%88%EF%BC%89/"/>
      <url>/2024/05/24/%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E8%B7%B3%E8%BF%9C%EF%BC%88%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E7%89%88%EF%BC%89/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>n你知道的，动态规划这个专题里面的题目不一定和动态规划有关。那为什么要把这个题目放在这个专题里面呢？是因为yg老师说这是动态规划的题目，虽然我看不出来这个题目跟动态规划有什么关系。</p><p>问题描述】</p><p>​    对于一个具有 *<strong>n*</strong> 个元素的数组 *<strong>a*</strong> , 执行以下操作：</p><ul><li>首先，选择下标 <strong><em>i*</em>* （1 ≤ *<strong>i*</strong> ≤</strong>*n*<strong>）—— 设置为数组的开始位置，放一个标记在 <em><strong>i*</strong> 处（值 为</em></strong>ai***）</li><li>当 *<strong>i*</strong> ≤ *<strong>n*</strong> 时，你的得分将增加 ***ai ，***且将标记向右移动 *<strong>ai*</strong> 个位置即下个位置是 *<strong>i*</strong> +*<strong>ai*</strong> ，继续这个过程直到 i&gt;n</li><li>如果 *<strong>i*</strong> &gt;***n，***则结束操作</li></ul><p>​    例如， 如果 <em><strong>n*</strong> &#x3D; 5且</em><strong>a*</strong>&#x3D;[7, 3, 1, 2, 3]，则可以进行以下操作</p><ul><li>选择 <em><strong>i*</strong> &#x3D; 1（</em>**a1***为7），操作过程为<img src="https://cg.hnu.edu.cn./cguserImages?_img=361e5bc5feb4ec9a0fb52b61626214ce.png" alt="img">，最后得分为 *<strong>a1*</strong> &#x3D; 7</li><li>选择 <em><strong>i*</strong> &#x3D; 2（</em>**a2***为3），操作过程为<img src="https://cg.hnu.edu.cn./cguserImages?_img=4301dff9867030141cf750c2245ca1dc.png" alt="img">, 最后得分为 *<strong>a2*</strong> + *<strong>a5*</strong> &#x3D; 6</li><li>选择 *<strong>i*</strong> &#x3D; 3，操作过程为<img src="https://cg.hnu.edu.cn./cguserImages?_img=98cfb4423753ec9da1b36a606f002857.png" alt="img">, 最后得分为 *<strong>a3*</strong> + *<strong>a4*</strong> &#x3D; 3</li><li>选择 *<strong>i*</strong> &#x3D; 4，操作过程为<img src="https://cg.hnu.edu.cn./cguserImages?_img=942e40dab178b0eb5fa39e594974ce08.png" alt="img">, 最后得分为 *<strong>a4*</strong> &#x3D; 2</li><li>选择 *<strong>i*</strong> &#x3D; 5，操作过程为<img src="https://cg.hnu.edu.cn./cguserImages?_img=646cf5cfca4b85071cfd25b68d4b9ae1.png" alt="img">, 最后得分为 *<strong>a5*</strong> &#x3D; 3</li></ul><p>​      请选择合适的开始位置，使得经过上述操作后可获得最大的分数。</p><p>【输入形式】</p><p>​      输入的第一行为一个整数 *<strong>t*</strong> (1≤ *<strong>t*</strong> ≤ 104)，表示测试用例的组数。</p><p>​      每个测试用例的第一行为一个整数 *<strong>n*</strong> (1≤ *<strong>n*</strong> ≤ 2×105)，表示数组 *<strong>a*</strong> 的元素个数</p><p>​      接下来一行包含 <strong><em>n*</em>* 个整数 *<strong>a1*<strong>、</strong>*a2**<em>、…、</em></strong>an*</strong> (1 ≤ ***a****<strong>i*</strong> ≤ 109)，表示数组 *<strong>a*</strong> 的元素</p><p>【输出形式】</p><p>   对于每个测试用例，输出独立一行，表示选择合适的开始位置后经过上述操作可以获得的最大分数。</p><p>【样例输入】</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">7 3 1 2 3</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">2 1 4</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">2 1000 2 3 995 1</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">1 1 1 1 1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>【样例输出】</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">1000</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>【判例说明】</p><p>   20%的测试数据 n≤10000 </p><p>   70%的测试数据 n≤100000 </p><p>   100%的测试数据 n≤200000 </p><p>题目大概就是这么个事儿，这个加强主要体现在测试数据部分，可以看到数据规模很大，如果直接暴力解题，或许很难全部通过。其实我一开始就知道暴力求解无法通过，但还是义无反顾地A了上去。你知道的，人就是这样，当然这样做也没错，毕竟很多事试试才知道，万一就成了呢?人不能失去尝试的勇气，就像只狼不能失去忍义手。</p><p>但是现实很残酷，只过了6组测试数据。于是我开始思考，怎么优化呢？首先想到的是提升I&#x2F;O流输入的性能，于是我添加了ios::sync_with_stdio(false);cin.tie(0);cout.tie(0);这一行代码，取消C++的I&#x2F;O库与C的I&#x2F;O库（即<code>stdio.h</code>）的同步，将cin和cout解绑。然而并没有什么卵用，还是只能通过6组测试数据。</p><p>看来只能从算法方面下手了啊，也是，原本时间复杂度接近O(n^2)的算法会超时是理所当然的。思索过后，我发现其实可以一边读入数据一边处理，于是就有了下面的代码。代码很简单，就算不写注释相信聪明的你也一定能看懂的🤗🤗🤗</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;cmath&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;cstring&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> arr[<span class="number">200010</span>]=&#123;<span class="number">0</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">ios::<span class="built_in">sync_with_stdio</span>(<span class="literal">false</span>);cin.<span class="built_in">tie</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);cout.<span class="built_in">tie</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> t,n,sum,tmp;</span><br><span class="line">cin&gt;&gt;t;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;t;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">memset</span>(arr,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="built_in">sizeof</span>(arr));</span><br><span class="line">cin&gt;&gt;n;</span><br><span class="line">sum=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> j=<span class="number">0</span>;j&lt;n;j++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">cin&gt;&gt;tmp;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(j+tmp&lt;n)</span><br><span class="line">    arr[j+tmp]=<span class="built_in">max</span>(arr[j+tmp],arr[j]+tmp);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">    sum=<span class="built_in">max</span>(sum,arr[j]+tmp);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">sum=<span class="built_in">max</span>(sum,arr[n<span class="number">-1</span>]);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d\n&quot;</span>,sum);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
