    <entry>
      <title></title>
      <link href="/2024/05/09/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B/"/>
      <url>/2024/05/09/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="我的故事"><a href="#我的故事" class="headerlink" title="我的故事"></a>我的故事</h1><p>一切的开或许是个意外，至少我爸妈是这么说的。</p><p>他们说当年有了我姐之后其实并没有生二胎的想法，但在机缘巧合之下，我来到了这个世界。小学三年级前的记忆太过模糊，像是我出生就是小学三年级一样。唯一残存在脑海中的画面也不过是我的父亲和一个大叔在路上攀谈罢了。</p><p>小学三年级又太过漫长，我一度以为自己这辈子都会是个三年级的小学生。当一辈子小学生也不错，那时候每天七点起床，刷个牙洗个脸，早餐一般是面条和粥，出门右拐走个两三步就到学校了。是真的就两三步，因为我家就在学校旁边。我的小学就算在暑假也不会关掉铃声，假期的时候也能听到上下课铃声。现在觉得是件很有意思的事，但那时候没啥感觉。要说三年级为什么难忘呢，说实话我也不知道为什么，只是之后的记忆再次模糊了起来。</p><p>那时候我家小区旁边就是一大片麦田，冬天的时候就是秃噜噜一片没啥好看的，但在春夏秋的景色都很不错。特别是秋天的时候，当风吹拂那片麦田，真像是一片绿色的海洋一样。</p><p><img src="https://tse3-mm.cn.bing.net/th/id/OIP-C.gAuy54cnkEc_UBlWp7_z0QHaEK?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain"></p><p>这张图片比较能给我那种感觉吧。虽然不是绿色的，我的麦田也没那么整齐。不如说反而是不整齐得有种美感，像是一只鲸鱼在我眼前遨游。</p><p>你知道的，很多学校上下学的时候都会放点音乐啥的。唯二给我留下印象的是“让我们荡起双桨”和My Heart Will Go On，荡起双桨就是要上学了，my heart go on了就是放学了。不知为何我想不起那时候的我的情绪了，开心或是悲伤呢，都不得而知。也可能因为太过年幼，所以莫得感情吧。</p><p>啊，突然之间就想起了好多好多，比如我第一次写作文被夸是因为我写了我们学校的浮雕，比如我们学校有个文化长廊，说是长廊其实感觉都不到50米，有一次我做梦的时候还给它加长了，比如我们学校提倡下象棋，然后我下课的时候的主要活动就变成了下象棋。有段时间我在我们班连战连胜，勾起了班里象棋天花板选手的兴趣，前来邀请我一决高下。我欣然应允，然后差点被吃成光杆司令。又想起学校新建的体育馆，我在哪里失去了我的一颗门牙。想起每年都有的叫啥来着，反正就是一帮人带东西到一个地方然后吃吃吃。我以为已经死去的回忆原来一直还存留在我的脑海中。唉，整挺好。</p><p>要说我人生中的第一个转折点（我自己认为），应该是在小学三年级的时候，不知道发什么癫参加了个什么卵奥数竞赛（当时类似海选，不少成绩相对好一点的学生去参加），然后居然还通过了。当我爸妈问我要不要继续下去的时候，我又不知道为什么选择了继续。是真的不知道为什么，因为其实我对数学没兴趣，上了中学之后数学一直是相对而言弱势的科目。然后我参加了奥数的，呃，应该叫兴趣班吧，一直上了两年。期间参加了三次还是四次来着，真记不清了，具体什么比赛也记不清了，只记得一次五千左右，去上海和天津比赛。唉，现在想想真觉得好坑钱啊。第一次去拿了个类似安慰奖的东西，第二次勇夺金牌！当然金牌不是唯一的，你懂的。第三次勇夺银牌！嘿你别说那奖牌是做得不错。不过我也很多年没见过了。其实我把这个事当成我人生的转折点不是因为我去学了奥数参加了比赛之类的原因，而是，因为去参加这个比赛，三年级的我就有了属于自己的手机。没错，我三年级就有了属于自己的手机哈哈哈哈哈哈。主要是因为去参加比赛毕竟是离开家人前往远方，就算有带队老师和同学，家长也肯定放不下心，所以我们去参加比赛的人基本都会带手机。而我爸妈的格局又比较大，干脆就直接给我了😁😁😁。</p><p>有了手机之后,年幼的我完全没有自制力(现在也没有),</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>生命在于运动</title>
      <link href="/2024/04/21/%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%8E%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8/"/>
      <url>/2024/04/21/%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%8E%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>z那天晚上刚刚下完小雨，空气很清新，机缘巧合下我时隔多年再次开始了乐跑，从宿舍跑到了大操场。那晚的麓山南路很拥挤，我只能在人群中穿梭前进，但内心还是迸发出一股喜悦感。或许阿嘉是对的吧，跑步时人体分泌出的多巴胺或许真的有打胶的时候的十倍呢。回到宿舍后我意犹未尽，也是不禁感叹世事难料，如果没发生那件事，我或许不会这么早就觉醒吧。</p><p>是啊，运动过后，我感觉自己像是大梦初醒，终于回到了现实。梦里我过得浑浑噩噩，而清醒过后我只觉得活着真是一件美好的事。我感觉时间的流速变慢了，又或许，是我变快了呢？啊，运动，我爱死它了。从那天起我就与运动坠入爱河了。运动真是爽爽爽爽！！！</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>词频统计</title>
      <link href="/2024/04/21/%E5%AD%97%E5%85%B8%E6%A0%91/"/>
      <url>/2024/04/21/%E5%AD%97%E5%85%B8%E6%A0%91/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>【问题描述】</p><p>  编写程序统计一个英文文本文件中每个单词的出现次数（词频统计），并将统计结果按单词出现频率由高至低输出到指定文件中。</p><p>  本题采用的数据结构为trie树，也称为字典树，具体请参考相关资料。</p><p>  注：在此单词为仅由字母组成的字符序列。包含大写字母的单词应将大写字母转换为小写字母后统计。此外，由于输入文件是英文小说，因此不会出现无意义的单词。</p><p>【输入形式】</p><p>  打开当前目录下文件in.txt，从中读取英文单词进行词频统计。</p><p>【输出形式】</p><p>  按单词出现次数由高至低输出前100个（不足100个按实际个数输出），每行输出一个单词及其出现次数，单词和其出现次数间由一个空格分隔</p><p>  也是一个让我很苦恼的题目，为了搞这题我学了字典树，本来还以为还要学多线程才能过，没想到只是稍微优化了一下就可以过了，果然也不能太相信ai写的代码啊。字典树这种数据结构对比线性结构确实有很大的优越性，不管是在空间方面还是时间方面。在这里实现的方法是类似邻接矩阵，开了一个二维数组来实现，然后开了个一维数组来存单词出现次数。还用了个哈希表来去重，感觉还挺猪鼻的，但是反正没人会仔细看，所以无所谓啦。上次实验报告我还特意写了另解，结果喜提69分，那还不如摆烂了，就酱吧。</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;unordered_map&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;cstring&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;vector&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;algorithm&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;fstream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;sstream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;cctype&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> n 10000</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Dtree</span>&#123;  <span class="comment">//字典树ADT </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> trie[n][<span class="number">26</span>];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> cont[n]=&#123;<span class="number">0</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> id=<span class="number">0</span>,sum=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">insert</span><span class="params">(string s)</span></span>&#123; <span class="comment">//插入函数 </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> p=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;<span class="built_in">int</span>(s.<span class="built_in">size</span>());i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> x=s[i]-<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(trie[p][x]==<span class="number">0</span>)trie[p][x]=++id;</span><br><span class="line">p=trie[p][x];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">cont[p]++;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">findcnt</span><span class="params">(string s)</span></span>&#123; <span class="comment">//查找函数被 </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> p=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;<span class="built_in">int</span>(s.<span class="built_in">size</span>());i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> x=s[i]-<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(trie[p][x]==<span class="number">0</span>)<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">p=trie[p][x];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> cont[p];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">unordered_map&lt;string,<span class="type">int</span>&gt;tip;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">isEnglishChar</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">char</span> c)</span> </span>&#123;  </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// ASCII码中，英文字符（包括大小写字母）的范围是65-90和97-122  </span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> (c &gt;= <span class="string">&#x27;A&#x27;</span> &amp;&amp; c &lt;= <span class="string">&#x27;Z&#x27;</span>) || (c &gt;= <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span> &amp;&amp; c &lt;= <span class="string">&#x27;z&#x27;</span>);  </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">comp</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">const</span> std::pair&lt;std::string, <span class="type">int</span>&gt;&amp; a, <span class="type">const</span> std::pair&lt;std::string, <span class="type">int</span>&gt;&amp; b)</span> </span>&#123;  </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 先比较int值  </span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (a.second != b.second) &#123;  </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> a.second &gt; b.second; <span class="comment">// 注意这里的符号，根据你的需求可能是 &gt; 或 &lt;  </span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;  </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 如果int值相等，则比较字符串的字典序  </span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> a.first &lt; b.first; <span class="comment">// 如果你想按照升序输出字符串，使用 &lt;  </span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 如果你想按照降序输出字符串，使用 &gt;  </span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">std::ifstream <span class="title">file</span><span class="params">(<span class="string">&quot;in.txt&quot;</span>)</span></span>; <span class="comment">// 打开文件  </span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (!file.<span class="built_in">is_open</span>()) &#123;  </span><br><span class="line">        std::cerr &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;无法打开文件!&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; std::endl;  </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">1</span>;  </span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    Dtree dt;</span><br><span class="line">string str;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">memset</span>(dt.trie,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="built_in">sizeof</span>(dt.trie));</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(file&gt;&gt;str)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">string pstr=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;<span class="built_in">int</span>(str.<span class="built_in">size</span>());i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">isEnglishChar</span>(str[i]))&#123;</span><br><span class="line">pstr+=<span class="built_in">tolower</span>(str[i]);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(!pstr.<span class="built_in">empty</span>())&#123;</span><br><span class="line">dt.<span class="built_in">insert</span>(pstr);</span><br><span class="line">        tip[pstr]=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        pstr=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">continue</span>;    </span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(!pstr.<span class="built_in">empty</span>())&#123;</span><br><span class="line">dt.<span class="built_in">insert</span>(pstr);</span><br><span class="line">tip[pstr]=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">file.<span class="built_in">close</span>();</span><br><span class="line">vector&lt;pair&lt;string, <span class="type">int</span>&gt;&gt;ve;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">const</span> <span class="keyword">auto</span>&amp; pair : tip)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">ve.<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(<span class="built_in">make_pair</span>(pair.first,dt.<span class="built_in">findcnt</span>(pair.first)));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sort</span>(ve.<span class="built_in">begin</span>(),ve.<span class="built_in">end</span>(),comp);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">const</span> <span class="keyword">auto</span>&amp; pair : ve)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(dt.sum==<span class="number">100</span>)<span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;pair.first&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>&lt;&lt;dt.<span class="built_in">findcnt</span>(pair.first)&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">dt.sum++;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
